
The KDVS News department is an independently run college radio news team.  All of our reporters are volunteers living in the city of Davis.  And certainly dont forget to tune into our broadcast at 90.3FM for our daily news briefs.  View our MySpace account at http://www.myspace.com/kdvsnewsdepartment to hear live streaming audio of our news broadcast from the KDVS station, directly through your computer.  Feel free to add us to your MySpace friends list.

